description: Sure we know who will win but watching these two battle it out is more than half the fun! The Sarge and Sarah Jane both bring their "A" game to WB on this visit. Sarge shows off his ever-growing bondage skills with some his hottest ties ever. Sarah Jane shows off her uncanny ability to take whatever is dished out to her. I wish I could show you some of the amazing almost haunting, underwater shots our photographers captured. But you'll have to join to see them. Great stuff you two! Come back and do it again sometime!
title: The Sarge vs Sarah Jane Ceylon
